dends and capital gains tax-free for middle-class families. </p><p><b>- governor (candidate last)'s plan will allow over 95% of american families to save and invest tax-free.</b> any taxpayer with adjusted gross income of under $200,000 would pay a tax rate of absolutely 0% on all of the income they earn from their savings, capital gains and dividends. </p><p><b>- with tax-free savings, more americans will join the investor class.</b> tax-free savings will encourage more families to build wealth by saving, investing and participating in the stock market, which will help grow the economy. </p><p><b>- <a href="http://www.(candidate full).com/news/press-releases/club_for_growth_comments">click here</a> to read governor (candidate last)'s plan to make middle-class savings tax-free.</b> </p><p><b> <u>letting the american people keep more of their hard-earned money:</u> </b> </p><p><b>governor (candidate last) has proposed a strong tax relief agenda.</b> governor (candidate last) will make the bush tax relief permanent, cut tax rates for all americans, abolish the death tax, and make the corporate tax rate more competitive with the rest of the world. </p><p><b>- <a href="http://(candidate full).com/img/pdf/ssa/6_challenge5_winning_the_global_economic_competition.pdf">click here</a> to read governor (candidate last)'s plan to cut taxes.</b> </p><p align="center"> <b>a stronger america and more support for our troops</b> </p><p align="center"> <b> <em>"(PARTY NAME)s for change believe in strength. we know that the best foe against tyrants and the best ally peace has ever known is a strong america."</em> – governor (candidate last)</b> </p><p><b> <u>strengthening our military:</u> </b> </p><p><b>governor (candidate last) will defend america by strengthening our military.</b> across america, there are thousands of families with members in the armed forces, reserves and national guard who need more support from washington. </p><p><b>- governor (candidate last) will add at least 100,000 more troops to our armed forces.</b> </p><p><b>- governor (candidate last) will commit at least 4% of our gross domestic product to defense.</b> this will help provide the resources needed for equipment, modernization, training, treatment and care of our wounded soldiers. </p><p><b>- <a href="http://(candidate full).com/img/pdf/ssa/2_challenge1_keeping_americans_safe.pdf">click here</a> to read governor (candidate last)'s full plan to strengthen our military.</b> </p><p><b> <u>defeating the jihadists: <br/></u> <br/> governor (candidate last) has outlined a comprehensive strategy to defeat terrorism and ensure american security.</b> as part of his global initiative for values and freedom, he will create the special partnership force built on a core of special forces experts trained to work with local governments around the world. </p><p><b>- <a href="http://(candidate full).com/img/pdf/ssa/3_challenge2_confronting_radical_jihad.pdf">click here</a> to view governor (candidate last)'s powerpoint on the special partnership force.</b> </p><p><b> <u>securing our borders:</u> </b> </p><p><b>governor (candidate last) will secure our borders and enforce our current immigration laws.</b> governor (candidate last) believes we must enforce our laws, secure our border, put in place an enforceable employment verification system, and provide no special pathway to citizenship for those here illegally. governor (candidate last) will cut back federal funding to cities that are "sanctuaries" for illegal immigrants and refuse to comply with federal law or aid federal law enforcement. </p><p><b>- <a href="http://(candidate full).com/img/pdf/ssa/9_challenge8_ending_the_tide_of_illegal_immigrants.pdf">click here</a> to read governor (candidate last)'s plan to enforce our immigration laws.</b> </p><p align="center"> <b>supporting stronger families</b> </p><p align="center"> <b> <em>"(PARTY NAME)s for change believe in strength. ... and we will strengthen the american family."</e